title: #184: Yellowman (@ShengWangTime, @BigJayOakerson)
itunes:title: Yellowman with Sheng Wang, Big Jay Oakerson
description: Sheng Wang came to my apartment to talk about the Asian American experience. Well, he came over to do a podcast, and then I asked him all about Chinatown, and then it just becomes a whole podcast about Asianness.
